    Dr. Yeriswamy is a consultant cardiologist in Bangalore having a rich
    experience in the management and treatment of heart diseases. He completed
    his MD in internal medicine and DM in cardiology after doing his MBBS and
    has been in practice ever since gaining a good exposure from his career.
    Some of the treatments carried out by Dr Yeriswamy are angiogram,
    hypertension, heart pump, coronary angioplasty, pacemaker implantation,
    blood pressure management and ECG. His treatments as a cardiologist involves
    the proper functioning of the heart and maintaining the required blood flow
    through the veins.
